<3  love the lyrics word by word <3  every line has deep meaning <3
"Tajdar- e -Haram", "ay kaatib -i taqdeer madeenah likh de",  "Kismat mein meri chain se jeena likh de "   

Understood only 10-20% lyrics when first heard it on star plus kulfi serial but still it touch my heart straight deep ! no matter if I am from different religion, the message was clear seeking the supreme divine.
Being a hindu  doesn't make much difference, listening to this kawali I visualize meeca and mata rani both <3
